00:08:21,817 --> 00:08:23,858
But we were making a destination-based experience

170
00:08:23,878 --> 00:08:25,779
that people could only realistically go through once.

171
00:08:26,299 --> 00:08:28,180
If we had accepted that sooner, we could have saved

172
00:08:28,200 --> 00:08:29,960
ourselves a ton of production time that might have been

