00:08:32,001 --> 00:08:34,442
You can still do service to that idea in a more shallow way,

175
00:08:34,522 --> 00:08:36,083
but without totally over committing your team.

176
00:08:36,783 --> 00:08:37,984
That is the end of the first aside.

177
00:08:39,585 --> 00:08:40,185
Narrative goals.

