00:24:49,313 --> 00:24:51,414
My parting thought, I think, is that the onus is on the

567
00:24:51,454 --> 00:24:53,535
content creator to present the user with something that feels

568
00:24:53,595 --> 00:24:54,676
intentional and concise.

